'''Nick Dudman''' was the Live Action Creature Effects Supervisor for several [[Lucasfilm]] productions such as ''[[Star Wars]]'' and [[Wikipedia:Indiana Jones|''Indiana Jones'']]. He helped create [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] and worked on make-up for [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']].

